Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.35,0:01:21.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真的是草摩同学的堂弟吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.05,0:01:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你和他感情好不好啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.16,0:01:27.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好可爱哟～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:27.69,0:01:29.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要来烦我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.33,0:01:35.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,夹…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.34,0:01:46.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.81,0:01:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你用用脑子再行动好不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.01,0:01:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你老是干傻事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.52,0:01:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会给我们添麻烦的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.92,0:01:55.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是开玩笑的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.55,0:01:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你居然读这种一大堆女孩子的学校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.56,0:02:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是每天担心不要变身、躲起来过日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.19,0:02:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干脆去读慊人指定的和尚学校不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.73,0:02:11.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只想踏出草摩家的大门
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.80,0:02:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,老鼠 你的想法我怎么可能会了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.51,0:02:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会赢的 我一定会赢过你的！！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.18,0:02:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢过你 堂堂正正的成为草摩家的一份子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.65,0:02:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我再也受不了你的耀武扬威了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:29.15,0:02:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我要赢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.59,0:02:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不…不行！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.46,0:02:39.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.83,0:02:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,再怎么生气也不能够打架啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.47,0:02:43.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架是不对的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是在学校里打架的话 不晓得会有什么状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啰唆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.21,0:02:50.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真啰唆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:50.91,0:02:51.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不管有什么状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.21,0:02:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我都要打败由希 这样就够了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别来妨碍我！搞什么东西嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.78,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是碍眼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.25,0:03:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,愤怒到了极点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.85,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我被他讨厌了 彻底被讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.53,0:03:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙 真是白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.33,0:03:13.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不打我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.86,0:03:16.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你还怕没有机会吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.57,0:03:31.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当神和十二只动物在深山里快乐地享受宴会的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.21,0:03:33.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫却在家里睡着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:34.09,0:03:38.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,作着有关根本不会举办宴会的隔天的美梦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.35,0:03:42.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我决定了 我不要属狗 我要属猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.59,0:03:45.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是我的真心话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.93,0:03:47.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我当时真的哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.63,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是有猫年同好会的话 我一定会加入的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.97,0:03:56.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…现在却被他讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.07,0:03:58.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.84,0:04:01.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不折不扣的笨蛋 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.98,0:04:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,接收到小透的电波信号
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.61,0:04:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.62,0:04:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你干嘛跪坐在那里？快上课了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.32,0:04:15.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好痛！痛死了 眼泪都…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.22,0:04:17.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不是啦 是刚刚撞到这个角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是看起来好像是她自己故意去撞的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.76,0:04:25.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以 你就跷课回来了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.97,0:04:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想离开这个家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才三天而已耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.71,0:04:33.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你要记住这也是修行 要好好忍耐才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.24,0:04:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我老是对那家伙说一些过分的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.15,0:04:40.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那家伙…你是指小透吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.98,0:04:43.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是不是又一副老样子大吼大叫了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.02,0:04:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然会后悔 当初何必大吼大叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.09,0:04:49.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你哦 真是可怜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.43,0:04:54.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不可能的 我不适合和别人一起生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.46,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然确实有这种人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:05:00.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过你的情况只是缺乏这方面的经验而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.47,0:05:06.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,举个例子好了 你可以一拳击碎桌子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.51,0:05:09.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是你也可以在击中之前住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.95,0:05:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是你对自己的力量的控制 不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.32,0:05:16.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你在山上和熊打过架 应该知道这种修行的成果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.15,0:05:18.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谁和熊打过架啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.55,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和人和睦相处也是相同的道理
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能只是在山上修行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.20,0:05:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须也在人群居住的城市里修行才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.70,0:05:35.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,必须从和人相处、伤害人以及被别人伤害中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.67,0:05:39.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从别人身上学习 自己也必须成长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.98,0:05:43.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,否则无法成为一个会为别人着想的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.58,0:05:47.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在武艺上你是黑带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.38,0:05:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但在和别人相处方面你只是白带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.09,0:05:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了有一天能够珍惜对你说喜欢你的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.19,0:05:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要逃避 继续修行吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.33,0:05:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么可能会有那种人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的有怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.43,0:06:06.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全无法想像 反正我也只是随口说说而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.34,0:06:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哦 是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.17,0:06:08.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.44,0:06:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨 回来啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.11,0:06:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.14,0:06:11.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她去打工
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.17,0:06:16.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她说回来的时候大概快11点了 我想去接她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.25,0:06:20.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去吧 这一带真的有色狼出没呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.29,0:06:25.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天也工作得很充实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.75,0:06:28.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家应该都睡了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.32,0:06:34.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹今晚应该又没有吃饭吧 还在生气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.63,0:06:36.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是又跑出去了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.57,0:06:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真是碍眼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.07,0:06:42.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉～该怎么办才好呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.41,0:06:45.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要表现得像自己一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.01,0:06:48.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会的 妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.34,0:06:49.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不会退缩的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.68,0:06:55.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这、这是什么声音!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.32,0:07:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.22,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这就是人家说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.99,0:07:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色狼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.59,0:07:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要啊～！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.10,0:07:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不能说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.00,0:07:16.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是他知道我把他误认为是色狼的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:16.84,0:07:17.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,实在太失礼了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.34,0:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是现在他一定彻底讨厌我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.38,0:07:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多多包涵 我的行为
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.92,0:07:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹先生你出来散步吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.22,0:07:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯…你喜欢学校吗…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:29.45,0:07:31.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,直接叫我就好了！不用加"先生"！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.16,0:07:35.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹…\N干嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.06,0:07:39.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 我只是叫看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.46,0:07:41.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事不要乱叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.46,0:07:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.73,0:07:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊…不 没关系 就算没事也可以叫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.04,0:07:50.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在我面前不用那么拘谨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.91,0:07:54.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要是有什么不高兴可以像刚刚那样揍我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.58,0:08:00.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,难道说 他是在为今天的事道歉？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.62,0:08:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以你今天才会来这里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.55,0:08:06.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来 那时候也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.12,0:08:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那时他是为了害我受伤而在道歉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.46,0:08:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我、我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.23,0:08:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉 你误会了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.03,0:08:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我会用书包打你是因为我把你当成色狼 所以才…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.57,0:08:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,色狼？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.43,0:08:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我绝对不是生你的气 其实我很喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.71,0:08:28.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很喜欢十二生肖的猫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是说 这个…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.05,0:08:33.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想跟你做好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果真的有怎么办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.22,0:08:38.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对你说喜欢你的女孩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.76,0:08:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,猫年没什么好的！快点回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像慢慢能够了解阿夹了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.90,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他比一般人迟钝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.67,0:09:00.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是他的本性很善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.88,0:09:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道要向别人道歉 真的很老实
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.45,0:09:12.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天是阿夹自己说要去接小透的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.02,0:09:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿～夹～是～个～大～色～鬼～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.52,0:09:17.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你唱那是什么东西！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.63,0:09:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,昨天是例外 以后没有了！再也不会有了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.36,0:09:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到你肯吃饭我很高兴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.87,0:09:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么样？合你的口味吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.41,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.18,0:09:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.08,0:09:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你刚刚干嘛看着我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.28,0:09:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看一下不行吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没事你看我干嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.88,0:09:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.95,0:09:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.92,0:09:41.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.63,0:09:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们来玩大贫民吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.93,0:09:59.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去找由希吧 混蛋由希
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.24,0:10:02.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不敢跟别人分个高下算什么男子汉嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.17,0:10:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉呀～真是没用～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来啊 分个高下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.21,0:10:09.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到时候你可别哭丧着一张脸～太妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.24,0:10:09.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,才不会呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.08,0:10:13.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,输的人要帮所有人做打扫工作哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:14.95,0:10:17.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么有一股愉快的电波呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:18.12,0:10:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次也找草摩同学吧！他到哪里去了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.96,0:10:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.66,0:10:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我现在不想和人交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我无法接受你的心意…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:33.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不！我不想听！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.64,0:10:35.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.24,0:10:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 这…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.88,0:10:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然很温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.49,0:10:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但总是拒人于千里之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.26,0:10:55.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家都这么说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.49,0:10:57.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希是很特别的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.56,0:11:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,普通的女孩并不适合你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.07,0:11:06.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}革命︰让牌的大小相反 三为最大 王牌最小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.14,0:11:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这家伙！居然来阴的！你这个臭男生！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,规则就是这样嘛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.94,0:11:11.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}有四张同样数字的牌就可以"革命"和"反革命"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.91,0:11:14.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,革命就是好牌会变烂牌
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,秘技 反革命！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.88,0:11:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,{\an8\fs20}反革命︰恢复牌原来的大小
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这下阿夹糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.82,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,干得好！花岛！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.12,0:11:24.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,唉 糗大了吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.92,0:11:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,少啰唆！胜负现在才要开始！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.39,0:11:34.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希你总是拒人于千里之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.91,0:11:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大贫民吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.34,0:11:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我知道规则
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.48,0:11:50.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是从来没玩过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.38,0:11:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是前不久才从小鱼那里学会的呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.22,0:11:56.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下次我们一起玩吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.05,0:11:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.92,0:12:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今天那家伙是大贫民罗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我来帮你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.66,0:12:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用！输了就是输了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.36,0:12:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是 我下次一定会赢回来！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当然 我也会赢你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.07,0:12:12.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你老是说这句话 不会腻吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.97,0:12:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢过你是我的信念！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.24,0:12:16.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是我的目标！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.37,0:12:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是你老是缠着我 却是我的麻烦 我的灾难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.91,0:12:22.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到你那副目中无人的样子我就一肚子气！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.88,0:12:25.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你那种短路的思考方式才让我一肚子火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.48,0:12:28.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又在吵架了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:28.75,0:12:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们是老鼠和猫 所以才会感情那么差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对了 前不久…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.13,0:12:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢过你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.39,0:12:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赢过你 成为草摩家的一份子！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.33,0:12:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他那句话的意思是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.13,0:12:45.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果赢过草摩同学的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.07,0:12:49.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就能加入十二生肖了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:50.31,0:12:51.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.61,0:12:56.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说来 加上猫就是十三生肖了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:56.21,0:12:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那真是太棒了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你这臭小子 看我揍扁你！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.55,0:13:04.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打架是不好的 不要打了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.29,0:13:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉悟吧！冷血的老鼠！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.36,0:13:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要一看到你 我的心情就很差
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.74,0:13:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 草摩同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.14,0:13:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么赢不了他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.71,0:13:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他今天下手特别重 真是个坏心眼的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.19,0:13:50.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许草摩同学他因为太在乎别人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.80,0:13:55.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以才会把自己的心情都掩饰起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.28,0:14:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快来看！外面有一个大美人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.31,0:14:08.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底是男生还是女生？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.62,0:14:11.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,讨厌 会不会是人妖啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.69,0:14:13.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,莫非是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.63,0:14:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:19.36,0:14:20.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗨 辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你、你特地来接我的吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 这么晚了 对一个女孩来说很危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.04,0:14:34.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,谢谢你 阿夹和你都好温柔哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.68,0:14:39.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好了 走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.62,0:14:42.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草、草摩同学！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.55,0:14:45.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.82,0:14:50.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果你有心事的话可以跟我说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.93,0:14:52.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.09,0:14:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人家说如果做恶梦的话 只要跟别人说就会有好事发生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.43,0:14:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你可以把你的坏心情让我分…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.27,0:15:02.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,年轻人别在这里鬼混 快回家去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.91,0:15:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我分担…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许我反而让你的心情更糟了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.25,0:15:19.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 是我不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.36,0:15:26.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当我还在本家的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.10,0:15:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像是在本家和慊人监视的笼子里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.53,0:15:35.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让我对被普通人围绕的普通生活充满了向往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.90,0:15:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才会离开家 进入男女同校的学校就读
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.61,0:15:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,结果我还是没有离开笼子 一样住在草摩家中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:48.08,0:15:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无法和一般人好好相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.19,0:15:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我并不想拒人于千里之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.72,0:15:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我还是…不够随和
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.76,0:16:05.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正因为如此 所以我的自卑和恐惧从未消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:07.44,0:16:09.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是阿夹就不一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.30,0:16:12.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然他的外表看起来很冲 可是如果习惯他之后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.34,0:16:14.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反而那种很吸引人的类型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.58,0:16:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我觉得就算他无法成为十二生肖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.11,0:16:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是能和一般人相处融洽也很不错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.62,0:16:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也想…像他一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.66,0:16:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以我才会觉得焦躁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.19,0:16:35.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要看到一心想进入草摩家的阿夹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.10,0:16:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我这个迫不及待想逃出来的人又算是什么呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.30,0:16:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你也有吸引人接近你的力量啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.51,0:16:46.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很多女孩都说喜欢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:46.78,0:16:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,觉得你很温柔呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.88,0:16:52.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我只是因为希望被别人喜欢 才表现出温柔的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.35,0:16:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就像想成为别人的朋友而请人吃点心一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.22,0:17:01.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只是为了自己才表现得温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许…该说是伪善吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:08.80,0:17:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,太突然了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.37,0:17:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,天气预告根本没说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.70,0:17:16.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了 咦？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.84,0:17:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,草摩同学～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事糟了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.01,0:17:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是田地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.95,0:17:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,应该说是家庭菜园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.68,0:17:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是你整理的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.69,0:17:32.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,嗯 这是我的秘密基地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.99,0:17:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好棒哦！原来如此！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.39,0:17:38.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你想保护秘密基地不被暴风雨侵袭吧是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.59,0:17:41.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我的力量很微薄 但是我愿意助你一臂之力！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.56,0:17:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你真善解人意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.20,0:17:46.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦 哪有啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是第一次有人这样说我呢 我好高兴哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.47,0:17:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,啊 可是 我会不会也是希望人家觉得我好才伪善的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不 我觉得你很自然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.41,0:18:01.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妈妈常说 与其怀疑人不如相信人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.08,0:18:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人不是一生下来就懂得温柔的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.92,0:18:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,人出生时只知道食欲、物欲等等欲望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.53,0:18:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,换句话说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:12.43,0:18:14.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就是只有求生的本能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.13,0:18:21.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,温柔是随着身体的成长一样在每个人的心中发育
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.27,0:18:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就是所谓的良心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:23.87,0:18:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以每个人的良心也会随着人的不同而有不同的形状
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.78,0:18:35.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,欲望是每个人与生俱来的 这点很容易理解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.55,0:18:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然而温柔却像是每个人亲手打造的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.82,0:18:41.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果被误解的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.19,0:18:44.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很容易就会被认为是伪善
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.26,0:18:47.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我听到这些话的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.23,0:18:53.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,心里想着良心可能会有圆形、栗子形 很兴奋呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.94,0:19:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你的温柔应该是蜡烛形的吧 有一盏明亮的灯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一这么想就会很高兴 打从心底开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.18,0:19:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为你是那么温柔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.25,0:19:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,比喻成蜡烛会不会很奇怪？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.42,0:19:09.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.92,0:19:13.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我实在太丢脸了 身为男生还这么放不开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.19,0:19:19.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很高兴呢 你告诉我那么多你的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.83,0:19:23.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,感觉我们的感情好像更好了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.87,0:19:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不好意思 继续执行保护基地的任务吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.84,0:19:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,每个人都很容易怀疑别人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.48,0:19:37.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是小透让人信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.25,0:19:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,成为一个值得信任的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:43.69,0:19:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你一定会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.79,0:19:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定会化身为别人的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.53,0:19:55.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拼命守护有成果了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.50,0:19:58.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是我们却变得这么狼狈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.40,0:20:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有没有什么可以采收了呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.94,0:20:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜 应该可以吃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.44,0:20:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,韭菜韭菜～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.11,0:20:07.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小透
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.91,0:20:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我下次…也想玩玩大贫民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.21,0:20:13.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,咦？好啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可是 你不是没有兴趣吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.08,0:20:21.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看你们玩得那么热闹 我也被吸引了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.36,0:20:23.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想试试看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.66,0:20:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就算是慢慢来也好 我想和大家融洽的相处
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.70,0:20:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.70,0:20:34.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小花和小鱼都是很好的人呢 她们是我引以为傲的朋友哦！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.60,0:20:39.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,而且你看起来那么厉害 大家一定会很高兴的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:41.71,0:20:43.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会输的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:50.72,0:20:55.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像是第一次看到草摩同学的笑容呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.33,0:21:03.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,让大家久等了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.13,0:21:05.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我最讨厌韭菜了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.73,0:21:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只是韭菜吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.07,0:21:08.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,葱和味噌你也讨厌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.74,0:21:10.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,味噌煮成汤就不讨厌了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.97,0:21:15.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不知道呢 不好意思 我再去做别的菜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:18.48,0:21:19.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃下去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.82,0:21:23.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们就是犯冲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.52,0:21:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么也改变不了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.15,0:21:32.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过 或许阿夹对由希也很羡慕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:32.46,0:21:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由希 阿夹已经昏过去了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:36.03,0:21:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果他们互相了解这一点的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:38.20,0:21:40.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,或许会变成好朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:41.54,0:21:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我好像误会你了 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:45.47,0:21:49.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也是 让我们永远做好朋友吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.28,0:21:54.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎么觉得…有点可怕

